 Junior]]){{efn|Original song by [[Lee Seung-hwan]], released in 1993.}}\n| length1 = 3:48\n| title2 = Confession Is Not Flashy\n| note2 = Inst.\n| music2 = Oh Tae-ho\n| length2 = 3:48\n| total_length = 7:36\n}}\n\n===Part 5===\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Released on {{start date|2020|4|10}}\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1 = Beautiful My Love\n| note1 = \uadf8\ub300 \uace0\uc6b4 \ub0b4 \uc0ac\ub791\n| lyrics1 = Yoon Min-seok\n| music1 = Yoon Min-seok\n| extra1 = [[Urban Zakapa]]{{efn|Original song by Lee Jeong-yeol, released in 1999.}}\n| length1 = 3:51\n| title2 = Beautiful My Love\n| note2 = Inst.\n| music2 = Yoon Min-seok\n| length2 = 3:51\n| total_length = 7:42\n}}\n\n===Part 6===\n{{tracklist\n| headline = Released on {{start date|2020|4|17}}\n| extra_column = Artist\n| title1 = In Front of City Hall at the Subway Station\n| note1 = \uc2dc\uccad \uc55e \uc9c0\ud558\ucca0 \uc5ed\uc5d0\uc11c\n| lyrics1 = Kim Chang-gi\n| music1 = Kim Chang-gi\n| extra1 = [[Kwak Jin-eon]]{{efn|Original song by Zoo, released in 1990.}}\n| length1 = 4:57\n| title2 = In Front of City Hall at the Subway Station\n| note2 = Inst.\n| music2 = Kim Chang-gi\n| length2 = 4:57\n| total_length = 9:54\n}}\n\n===Chart performance===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:24em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:2em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\"| Peak<br />positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5em;\" | Remarks\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Ref.\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Gaon Digital Chart|KOR]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lonely Night\" <small>([[Kwon Jin-ah]])</small>\n| rowspan=5| 2020\n| 83\n| Part 1\n| rowspan=5| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=ALL&targetTime=15&hitYear=2020&termGbn=week|title=2020 Week 15 Digital Chart|accessdate=April 16, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"In